      ],
      "message": "wallet: Drain validation interface queue after notifications disconnect\n\nWhen unloading a wallet, there may be unexecuted callbacks in the\nvalidation interface queue that can still execute after we have\ncompleted all of the other wallet shutdown tasks. Instead of letting\nthese run in the background, once the notifications are disconnected,\nwait for the queue to drain before continuing with wallet shutdown.",
      "committer": {
        "name": "Ava Chow",
        "email": "github@achow101.com",
        "date": "2026-02-20T22:57:16Z"
      },
